### Categories API Endpoints

### Get All Categories (Default: sorted by name, ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get Categories sorted by Count (Descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories?sort=count&order=desc&include_stats=true
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get Categories sorted by Name (Ascending) without Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories?sort=name&order=asc&include_stats=false
Accept: {{contentType}}
